                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130714-16-off96 t18130714-16-cd97"></join>, a watch, value 30 s. a watch-chain, value 3 d. a seal, value 6 d. a watch-key, value 1 d. a coat, value 1 l. a pair of breeches, value 5 s. and a shirt, value 2 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
